{
  "stem": "20084.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 41.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, at that time already, they started to liquidate the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It means they were coming at night with lists, certain people, to-- to take them out on transport.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't know where they were going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the SS, with the Jewish Police together, they were making the list up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was-- you couldn't get out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You couldn't get out in the street to-- you know, you were trying to get something, get bread or some food or something.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You were trying to get out of the ghetto, to buy something from smugglers or get out and buy-- buy some food, something, to sell for jewelry or something, whatever you had.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Time were getting very tough.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was hard to get food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We all had to register, register to get the-- the ration book.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was a official document which was called the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was a German document with your photo on it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The round outs.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All the round outs, all the roundups at night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't sleep at night.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in the daytime, we had to go to work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I worked on-- at the brick factory.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And going out to Bonarka, I worked, that time, on the loading up-- loading up-- loading bricks.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you worked with a spade, with a spade cutting out blocks of lime from the fields, and putting it in-- into a wagon, which was on the rails.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this was very hard work, just to lift up a block that you cut out-- cut out with a spade.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was like very soft, like clay.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But it was very heavy work, very heavy work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the Germans were there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The guards were there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There were also guards, Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There were Lithuanian guards.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
